// ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
//  LOKI DEV LAYOUT - Claude Code + Terminals
// ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

layout {
    default_tab_template {
        pane size=1 borderless=true {
            plugin location="compact-bar"
        }
        children
    }

    // Main dev tab - Claude Code dominates
    tab name="claude" focus=true {
        pane split_direction="vertical" {
            // Claude Code - the brain (70% width)
            pane size="70%" name="claude" {
                command "claude"
            }
            // Right side - stacked terminals
            pane split_direction="horizontal" {
                // Top: shell for quick commands
                pane name="shell"
                // Bottom: logs/watch
                pane name="logs"
            }
        }
    }

    // Second tab - pure terminal workspace
    tab name="term" {
        pane split_direction="horizontal" {
            pane name="main"
            pane split_direction="vertical" {
                pane name="aux1"
                pane name="aux2"
            }
        }
    }

    // Third tab - git focus
    tab name="git" {
        pane {
            command "lazygit"
        }
    }
}
